aṭas n yigduden ara d-iɣlin ddaw uḍar-ik
meẓyan yeffeɣ-d d argaz iẓewren di ṣṣyada iḥemmel lexlawi
tura winna iruḥ ad yeẓẓal neɣ ad d-yaker
wid iǧehden ttawḍen tmanyin n yiseggasen
uraret s ugrambi ḥlawen akked lɛud
war ccek kemm d timsewwit yelhan
saɛid u muḥ yerra-d ṭṭlem meṛṛa ɣef tiziri tagawawt
win inehhun leǧnas ɛni ur ittɛaqab ara
annaɣ a sidi ṛebbi err-iyi ɣer taddart
tom yuzen-as i mary takarḍa n umulli
ad imsenḍaḥ s uniyir-s akked upulis
ilul deg kityum yiwet n teɣremt tagrikit zedɣen deg tuget yefniqiyen
ugur-nwen netta d teɣzef n yiles
i sebɛa yid-sen d dderya i s-d-tesɛa bilha i si mḥemmed
tezmer ad k-d-tefk afus n tallalt
qqlet-d ɣer uxxam ma ulac aɣilif
d acu ay tenniḍ deg wetriku-a
ɛecra imeḥbas i irewlen si lḥebs
ur zmireɣ ad d-rreɣ ɣef tuttra-a
sima ur as-iɛedda ara wayen i as-d-yenna maziɣ kan akka
ur rǧiɣ ara ad ttwaferneɣ imi d asentel i yellan d aṭabu deg tmetti-nneɣ i ɣef i d-uriɣ
maca nettat simmal tettimɣur simmal yettban-d deg-s umgarad i ɣef tmetti tawacult d tizya-s
maɣef d yidir umi nnant d amezwaru
yuba yessasen wasila n qasi mḥemmed n at yusef i imawlan-is
iwweḥhel-iyi wawal di tgerjumt seg akken ttaggadeɣ
ihi iban kan yeqqim deg uxxam
idammen-is rekkmen am useqqi di teccuyt
amdan d amedya n ṣsber ur d-yessugun yiwen deg ugama
iɣaḍ yelli-s n ferɛun tenna d yiwen seg warrac n iɛebṛaniyen
d yiwen i d-yeǧǧan leqdic meqqren u mazal yezmer ad yeqdec sya ar sdat
fiḥel asḥisef yal wa d acu i t-ixuṣen
d taqbaylit i lemden ar yemma-tsen
yeḍra-d iḍelli deg iḍ kra yeffɣen i tannumi
tin yebɣan ad tagi ad tagi
tadwilt i d-yellan i lfayda n snat twinas n yiselmaden n lwilayat n umalu n tmurt
asentel iɣef tettezzi tmedyezt-iw d tilelli n umeslay
ur nezmir ad nedder war lhawa
d amelsi yerna anagi ur t-yesɛi
yessexreb-as targit-is ur yebni ara ɣef wannect-a
yeẓra-tt tettru ɣef nnbi yuɣ-itt dɣa tbeddel-it s wayeḍ
ad as-tiniḍ llan aṭas aṭas n yetran
nella neɣleb yiwet n tlefsa n ddabex uḍar
leɣmiq isawal i leɣmiq s ṣṣut n icercuren-ik
taqerbust tendeh tmes deg yiwen n yiger
ikellex-as zzman ur yeẓri ansi s-tufeg
ur tezmireḍ ad tgeḍ laman deg sliman u saɛid amezdat
rrus d tamurt i d-yezgan gar sin n yimenẓawen turuft akked asya
snat n ddqayeq ad d-iliɣ din
nna ḍrifa teɣra cwiṭ ar yimṛabḍen n iṛumyen
ar ɣas werǧin i ɣer ḥedd neɣ i telliḍ d asaxi
maca d izegrawen aṭas neɣ uhu
ur ttaǧǧa ara taydit ad d-tadef
tella tin i d-iẓeḍmen ɣef tom
ɣef wammud n yisefra n mexluf n at qasi u sɛid
ad fken medden wissen acu iwakken kan ad d-ḥessen i tmeɣra n ccna seg imukan am widak
zemreɣ ad dduɣ yid-k ɣer unafag
ad d-yas yuba ad iqelleb fell-ak
mi kem-sɛiɣ yid-i ul-iw yess-m yetwennes
d win iwumi i zeddigit yifassen
qqlen-d ɣer uxxam uqbel tis tamet
alluy n tɣalltin d addal yelhan
riɣ ad ffɣeɣ ad ččeɣ deg yiḍ-a
deffir-sent tecna-d tlemẓit bundawi anya tizlit-nni n malika dumran
ad berrḥeɣ s nnṣaḥa-k akked leslak-ik
ass n lḥedd ɣef ttnac n uzal
ur tebɣi ara ad tehder yid-i tura yerna ur ẓriɣ ara acimi
ayen i d-ixeddmen kra n temsirin ɣef tfizikt taɣisant
ur cukkeɣ ara d yuba i tt-ixedmen
ad ɣiwleɣ ad rewleɣ i waḍu iǧehden
issufɣ-it ɣer beṛṛa inna-yas muqel igenni
ad t-yeḍfer s telqey deg yal taɣult
imdanen n tɣiwant-a d wid ikerhen adfel
iban yella kra n ssebba yellan
ttif win iṭṭfen wala win ibran
ma tqebleḍ bɣiɣ ad as-fkeɣ axeddim
anda yella ubduz iqerben ɣer da
ḥemmleɣ tizlit talwit n smail kessay
ayen yellan sdaxel yettfaka mi ara tbelleɛ adlis
yuba yessuter seg tiziri ad t-taɣ
ur bniɣ fell-ak ad d-taseḍ ɣer da
ur ssineɣ aṭas n tɣawsiwin fell-ak
jane ur telli teẓra tiziri tezwej
maɣef ay bɣan yiwen seg widak
yiwet n tikkelt i tettɛedday ɣef wuccen
buṛǧ buɛrirej d tamdint taqbaylit tezga-d ar tama n unẓul asamar n bgayet
ur yezmir ara ad d-isali azegrir n ukter n imedlis n tensa
yuba u muḥ ur yessiwel ara i tiziri tagawawt
ladɣa deg uḥric n tussniwin n tmetti taqbaylit i icudden ɣer yinig
d win i d amenzu i tessider
aksum s tefses ay yebḍa ɣef yiɣsan
yettemlaqa d umeddakel-is ɣer taggara n wass akken ad qqimen
maɣef ay teqqimemt deg uxxam iḍelli
axaṭer akken i tettḥasabem ara tettuḥasbem
ur ufint ara abrid i adem d ṛebbi-s i tent-yesseknan
yal mi ara nennaɣ qqareɣ-as wellah ma tɛawed-as
llan aṭas n yefriqiyen deg lalman
acḥal aɛeni yak-xelleṣen i wannect-a agi tgiḍ
ur ɣlay ara wučči deg usečču-ihin
tessefhem-it acuɣer ur tezmir ad terzu ɣur-s
neɣ lḥeqq-ik di tmurt n tatut
tella kra n yiwet i tebɣiḍ ad twaliḍ
acu kan llant yessi-s n lilit
wissen ma ahat ad yezzi wass ad yettu ayen yeḍran yid-s
iɛedda waggur segmi i ssneɣ kahina
d ul-iw i tt-ibɣan mačči d nekkini
umuɣ n yisenfaren i d aɣ-d-ikecmen yugar ayen nurǧa
ur cukkeɣ ara ad t-id-qeblen ad iɣer taglizit deg tesdawit
bɣan ad jeggren tamurt s wudem abeṛṛani
iyyat ad neddu srid ɣer teftist
i kunwi d acu i kwen-id-igren di tessirt
ala ɣef telt-yyam i yecfa lewnis deg leɛmer-is
ur bɣiɣ ad dduɣ s aɣerbaz ass-a
am wakken ur ttmeslayen ara yiwet n tutlayt
ayɣer i txemmem la ttxemmimeɣ fell-awen
s tira kan i zemreɣ ad beyyneɣ tudret-iw
wid i d-yufraren deg teẓrigt-agi tamaynut
ah tagi d tamsalt-nniḍen d agama i k-id-yefkan akka ɣas ɣef wannect-a ur yecni lewnis
arraz n aysat rabaḥ n tezdeg deg uḥric n useḥbiber ɣef twennaḍt
tiziri ur tufi d acu ara as-tini
ad idiren akken jmiɛ beɛden ɣef lmeḥna d wurfan
llan yexxamen umezgun isalayen timkarḍayin d wurtiyen deg temdint-a
yettraǧu-tt ɣer tewwurt ma tgumma ad as-teldi am uqjun yettɛassan ɣef bab-is
ladɣa ayen i icudden ɣer tarrayin n unadi ɣer yinig
seg yigenwan illu imuqqel-d s imdanen
iha iha a mm imezran ɣer waggus
acḥal yellan n yitran deg igenni
ur ttnalleɣ ara tiɛelǧtin iyi-d-yettaɣ baba
maɣef ur teɣriḍ i kra n yiwen
win icerwen tidiwin yeṣber ur yettaf tifrat
ula d iẓerman n uɛebbuḍ ttnaɣen
ttawilat n zzwayel am tbarda ṣṣrima aleggam azenbil
ah ihi akka ay tetteẓẓgemt tafunast
ad d-yeldi inuba tawwurt ad ibed din s uqrab ɣef tuyat-is
ul-iw ijreḥ ɣer daxel i tent-yuɣ
waqila aṭas ara ihelken mi ara teḥlu tutlayt taqbaylit
iwakken iḥeqqiyen ur ggaren ara ifassen-nsen di lbaṭel
nezmer ad d-nini tura yewjed walbum
amcum issemɣar iman-is ur ittcawar ara
nekk ad iliɣ di laman ad theddneɣ
tiktabin mbezrurɛent ta tefteḥ ta temdel ta ɣef yiri qrib ad teɣli
am wakken i kettben medden tiɣawsiwin
d aseɛdi lǧens i t-yesɛan d agellid
tlaq-as tebɣest i si ḥmed waɛli
anwa i ileḥqen abrid s tikli
yella win i s-iluɛan i tom
ad ilint deg-s am dima tezlatin n umennuɣ akked tiyaḍ
kra xedmeɣ n lxiṛ yuɣal-d d ixmiṛ
iweṣṣa tom yiwen ara s-d-ixedmen ad yečč
ur fhimeɣ ara anamek n tnelli-nni uqbel taneggarut
isallen qqaren-d katia tugi ad tdel iman-is
zik deg ssuq i ttemyakken yimdanen ttiɛad
ad d-tafeḍ kra n tɣawsa ara m-d-iɛeǧben
azal n ddurt aya d udfel yekkat
i d-yenna uselway n tdukkla numidya mass saɛid zeɛmuc
ad bɣunt ad cfunt ɣef waya
lahlak-is izmer ad yili d akunsir
tafyirt-nni ur ssawaḍeɣ ara ad tt-fehmeɣ alma zziɣ-tt acḥal n yiberdan deg wallaɣ-iw
am win yettaken irden i yir tuɣmas
ur ttruḥuɣ ara ssya ɣas ulamma ad sɛeddiɣ iḍ dagi alamma d ṣṣbeḥ
nneɛma akked leḥmala-k ad tteddunt yid-i
anwa ay d aselmad-nwen n tanglizit
iɛac yuba da tlatin n iseggasen
ma d wid yenɛel ad ttwakksen seg-s
yidir yerra-tt ḥaca i tunḍa deg ussu-s
tuɣeḍ tanumi ad truḥeḍ ɣer iɛekkuren
s lemɛawna n yillu ad nesɛu leɣlab
tecfa ɣef umkan i yella iḍelli
d aymi i d-reggleɣ ɣer umezgun
ur ttsetḥi ara s wayen i telliḍ
medden akk ḥemmlen ddabex n uḍar
limer ass-a mačči d amerḍil amzun d laɛwacer ahat yiwen ur t-id-tettadder
d wayen-nniḍen i yecban tayda akerruc axerrub aṣefṣaf acekrid anagar asɣar n yifites
ad iruḥ beẓẓa fell-as asmi ara teḥreṣ
iḥucc-d aslen akked wulmu i wakraren-is
s cwiṭ kan n wafud ad yili s tidett
d acu i la teqqaṛemt tura akka
ur tt-id-iṣaḥ ad terr awal ma ur tt-yeɛǧib
d acu i yebɣa ad d-yini
ad ɛeddiḍ tikkelt kan f ubrid dɣa ad cfuɣ fell-as
kerheɣ lexdayem n wid yeffɣen i ubrid
ladɣa deg yidgan i d-yezzin i wammasen n usɛeddi n yikayaden
tbeddel i lqedd-iw tikli kul ass fell-i d asemmiḍ
abrid-is mluza lmadani lqedd n usaru
arnaflas d win ur nettamen s tilin n kra n yillu
aṭas i teglalzeḍ deg wannar n taddart
iḍelli nruḥ nekk d tmeṭṭut-iw ɣer uxxam umezgun
gar wayen yelhan di tudert d cwiṭ n tseddarit
yeẓra d tasusmi kan i yeḥwaǧ
d tamurt-nni kan i sɛan d ayla-nsen
ulac laman di bu sin n yiḍarren
acḥal n tikkal ay twalam aya
yal ass yettawi-d amur-is n tekriḍt lmut lejruḥ lbumbat leḥbus timenfi
ulac tasdawit deg umaḍal ur neqqar ara fell-as
d nekk s yiman-iw ara s-ibedden
ur zmireɣ ara ad ttuɣ ass-nni
imaswaḍen si tama-nsen mmeslayen ugar ɣef tɣessa akked talɣa n uḍris
wissen d acu i tt-id-yewwin gar-asen
d acu ay k-id-yewwin deg lweqt-a
ula d ijiṛmeḍ d mmis n tmurt
d acu ay tga taninna din
akken yebɣu yili wugur ɣur-s tifrat
nɣan akk tid ur yettlusun ara lḥijab
aɣyul yusa-d kan ad issuter awal imi yeḥṣa d awal i d tafat
ur fhimeɣ ara taluft-a d acu-tt
katia truḥ d asfel d asfel i tmetti tatrart
ad ten-tbeddleḍ akken i tettwabeddal llebsa
nekk ad ferneɣ ad iliɣ feṛḥeɣ
tasuta n tmanyin ɣef tmaziɣt i twet mačči ɣef teqbaylit
yendem ɛmeṛ d ṭṭbel deḥman imerreg-itt xaled ẓemmer ceɛban
tikeṛyas d lligat d llebsa iceṭṭiḍen atg
afus ayeffus n umeɣlal isbeyyen-d tazmert-is
ur zmireɣ ara ad dduɣ yid-k
iwacu i d-iḍerru wayen n diri i wid yelhan
d acu ay la d-yettheggi yidir
d kečč s timmad-ik i d amasay n yiɣeblan-ik akken ma llan
mi yinifif-nni yegra-d uxxam-nsen d axrib
ad yenfeḍ ula d ciṭ yebnan
ur bɣiɣ ara s yisem n ddin ad d-ikkat ugeffur n yimeṭṭi
maɣef ay ira yuba yidir anect-a akk
ilaq ad yi-tɛawnem i wakken ad ten-id-nsellek
ad ṭṭseɣ yiwen n yiḍes d aẓayan
i taseḍ-d ɣef tizi n tis sḍiset
di kra n wagguren kan teɣli tdamsa n tmurt-a
ur qqimeɣ ara akken war axxam
ass-a ad nečč imekli deg beṛṛa
tamexluqt n ṛebbi ur teṭṭif deg yiman-is
daffy duck d nniyya kan zgan ttkellixen-t
acimi ur nezmir ara ad nečč dagi
txeddem i imeẓla uffiren n fransa
cikkeɣ yella kan yiwen n wugur
hatan d ayen i tebɣiḍ neɣ ala
taxxamt-nni ideg yeggan teččur d izan
tasnasɣalt-inu mazal-itt ɣer farid n at yiraten
beṛkat ur ttṛebibbet ara ɣef wanwa i tettkellixem
nekk d amṛabeḍ i ken-ittarran d imqeddsen
ulac akk ayen i yifen idrimen
ḥsen u muḥ yuɣal yeqreb ɣer tiziri tagawawt
ula d tasnasɣalt n yuba tettwaker
ɣur-i tura setta n wagguren nekk ttruḥeɣ ɣer tzeqqa n waddal
mmi-s n udrar ḥmed ṛebbi d amaziɣ cfu ɣef laṣel-ik
tebda s ugdal n yiɛeggalen n tseqqamut n ugezdu-a timlilit n yiselmaden
lukan mačči deg tebɣest i txu a-t-an tesmar-as-d akk ayen tesɛa
yessaram ad ad ibeddel timuɣliwin alukan deg taɣult-is kan
mi ur d-yettɣimi kra n ccɣel ara tgem d acu ay tettgem
ad yili d aqeddac n iqeddacen n watmaten-is
am wakken ma mačči s tefransist i yesselmad mačči d tamussni
tesɛedda-d akk ayen ur yezmir umdan ad yerfed
d atay ara teswed neɣ d taɣlust
tella kra n tɣawsa i ixuṣṣen
d kečč i d nnṣib-iw di ddunit-a
yuba ur yessawaḍ igerdan s aɣerbaz
tella tin i yettṛaju ɛemmi muḥ
d yuba ay tebɣiḍ ad teẓreḍ
ddeqs aya segmi ur ttemlaɛint ara
ffɣet-aɣ ay at ɛziz teɛṛeq yemma d yemmat-wen
iwakken ad rzun ɣer umḍiq ideg yeḍra yiwen n usehwu deg ubrid aɣelnaw wis setta u deg rmila
acemma kan ad tenceɛ ɣef uneɛneɛ
am win yefuden yeswa akka i teḍra yid-i
wid akk i iyi-d-ittwalin ttihiyen fell-i
ssefqed ma teɣriḍ-d tafyirt akken iwata
ddukklen di sin armi d tameddit nsan di n taddart
tagi d win akken yiwen ur d-yettmeslay fell-as deg taddart
ayɣer i tunfeḍ makken i t-id-temlaleḍ
wagi d acqirrew ɣef wid yakk i as-iqqaren d akken taqbaylit ur tezmir ara i tussna

amdan yeṣfan izmer ad yečč seg weksum-nni

setta n wussan ara txeddmeḍ lecɣal-ik
akken ara kecmeɣ usu ad ṭṭseɣ di lehna

ma nniɣ ad xedmeɣ am nutni
nqarr-d d nekkenti ay yenɣan zakiya n tɛeccact
ad nuɣal yal ma ara as-nsell i nnaqus ad neḥṣu yis-s ad nerwel
tifyar n tiziri sehlent i usuqqel
sexdem amawal n yal ass axir
daymi i d-thegga isragen uziggen n tɣuri d uwehhi n yiselmaden-a
ferruǧa d yiwet n teḥdayt i as-yettilin
ameɣlal ad d-iceggeɛ si ṣiyun aɛekkaz n leḥkem-ik
mbeɛb irna-d gma-s afus-is iṭṭef deg ugerz n meẓyan
di lbabur d teflukin ad yesserkeb sut tura

d temẓi i ixeddmen ɣef temɣer
feṛḥeɣ nezzeh s warraz i d-yettunefken sɣur tddukkla adrar n fad
i nessaram d tujjya i kra yellan d amuḍin
yemma-s n cookie temmut s ufurray
yiwen ur yecliɛ anwa i kem-ilan
tura akka aṭas i yettmesteqsayen ma yella ai-da d tanaẓurt
bexlaf ṭṭir lḥur d ɛebderreḥman umira
ula d yuba d amẓawan uẓwir mliḥ
i wacu ay la tlemmdeḍ tanglizit
ur ilaq ara ad teqqimem da
assa ur nekfi ara abrid s tikli mi aɣ-yefka yinijjel i yifri
awi-aɣ-d sin ifenǧalen n lqahwa ttxil-k
ula d internet ikcem ixxamen tura
isetḥa yidir ad as-yini i newwara

armi medlen allen ɣef lbaṭel i ttwalin

anwa i yerẓan tazewwut d netta

yuba yusa-d ad imudd afus i wrida n at qasi muḥ

nezmer ad nehder ɣef ayen yeḍran ass-nni

teɣli-d s wawal ur nlaq ara sdat urgaz-is
